### Tlcpl by byn.
Introducing TLCPL by byn. Tlcpl, or the Toledo Lucas-County Public Library, is a library system in Northwestern Ohio. Tlcpl by byn is a new, wonderful app for you to get to what you need, fast through TLCPL. 

![Tlcpl Screenshot](https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/LXg30_liwKEutf5-vb56omq7xAe5sOM5tVVcrsY0kcEkg-tr6tIOeyutnYoTH8684DfvyQBC1IQ)

Get it all from Aerobyn.
tagline: A new simple way to what you want from TLCPL
